cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in published research, please cite it as below."
title: "AFM Similarity Search"
abstract: >
  A multimodal similarity search tool for Atomic Force Microscopy (AFM) images,
  combining BiomedCLIP image embeddings, MatBERT NER metadata extraction, and
  PostgreSQL + pgvector for retrieval.
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-05-05"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/gvelard2/AFM_VectorSearch"
authors:
